{"tid":530270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯判囚】63歲女子庭外辱罵裁判官 涉藐視法庭被捕","createTime":"2018-01-15T14:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T02:37:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":104,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"10ac64e59e0e5a9fee4c335bd96aecb9edf3fd95","tid":530270,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"退休警司朱經緯在佔領期間以警棍擊傷途人罪成，早前被判囚3個月，一群支持朱的撐警人士發起遊行，並把矛頭直指印度出生的主審裁判官錢禮，在庭外辱罵她。警方於早前接獲相關轉介，指有人於1月3日在東區裁判法院外，涉嫌向司法人員作出不當及侮辱性言論，港島總區公眾活動調查組經調查後，今日在北角區拘捕一名63歲姓郭女子，涉嫌藐視法庭。被捕女子已獲准保釋候查，須於2月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥日前出席行會前曾表示，會堅定捍衞司法獨立，對於侮辱、恐嚇法官的行為不能接受，社會不會容忍，會依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180115/57711895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57711895&d=IpVAHYfqpalG2qdNe%2B3tkwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=42016046\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57711895&h=fd970895\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180115/57711895</a>"},{"pid":"52b1303f4f307c8f0f4b583dd312b67bdb4293e7","tid":530270,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"最後武士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ee3f93eee068654d3c2d9a9b6967fad5df0b7f","tid":530270,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"法官拉人，法官放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b4dca57db813fe398ee1a6c516a7dbc6619584","tid":530270,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15: